{"text_id":118644,"tokens":["Online"," learning"," has"," revolution","ized"," education"," and"," enables"," students"," with"," limited"," time"," and"," resources"," the"," chance"," to"," pursue"," an"," education"," without"," attending"," traditional"," schools","."," With"," this"," burgeoning"," field"," of"," study"," comes"," a"," range"," of"," advantages"," and"," disadvantages"," that"," students"," must"," consider"," when"," deciding"," whether"," or"," not"," to"," pursue"," online"," learning","."," The"," advantages"," include"," flexibility",","," cost"," effectiveness",","," convenience",","," and"," the"," ability"," to"," pursue"," specialized"," tracks","."," On"," the"," other"," hand",","," the"," disadvantages"," include"," lack"," of"," networking"," opportunities",","," lack"," of"," academic"," resources",","," and"," lack"," of"," human"," interaction",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," primary"," advantages"," associated"," with"," online"," learning"," is"," the"," flexibility"," it"," offers","."," Online"," learning"," is"," available"," anytime"," and"," from"," anywhere","."," This"," makes"," it"," ideal"," for"," students"," who"," are"," juggling"," jobs",","," family"," obligations",","," and"," other"," commitments"," that"," make"," it"," difficult"," to"," attend"," traditional"," schools","."," Additionally",","," online"," learning"," provides"," students"," with"," access"," to"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," courses"," that"," they"," may"," otherwise"," not"," be"," able"," to"," pursue","."," This"," flexibility"," allows"," students"," to"," customize"," their"," education"," to"," meet"," their"," particular"," goals"," and"," interests",".","\n\n","Another"," advantage"," of"," online"," learning"," is"," cost","-","effectiveness","."," Because"," it"," typically"," does"," not"," require"," physical"," structures"," or"," textbooks",","," the"," cost"," of"," online"," learning"," can"," be"," considerably"," lower"," than"," traditional"," education","."," This"," is"," especially"," beneficial"," for"," students"," with"," limited"," financial"," resources","."," In"," addition",","," online"," learning"," can"," be"," accelerated"," so"," that"," students"," can"," complete"," their"," studies"," at"," a"," faster"," pace","."," This"," also"," helps"," students"," save"," money"," on"," tuition"," fees",".","\n\n","The"," convenience"," of"," online"," learning"," is"," another"," attractive"," feature","."," Students"," can"," complete"," assignments"," from"," the"," comfort"," of"," their"," own"," home"," or"," on"," the"," go","."," Studies"," can"," be"," conducted"," at"," any"," time"," of"," day"," or"," night",","," enabling"," students"," to"," fit"," study"," sessions"," into"," their"," own"," individual"," schedule","."," Additionally",","," many"," online"," courses"," offer"," asynchronous"," learning",","," meaning"," that"," students"," can"," access"," course"," material"," at"," their"," own"," pace",".","\n\n","However",","," there"," are"," certain"," drawbacks"," to"," online"," learning"," as"," well","."," One"," of"," the"," primary"," disadvantages"," is"," a"," lack"," of"," networking"," opportunities","."," While"," online"," networking"," is"," becoming"," more"," commonplace",","," it"," does"," not"," provide"," the"," same"," level"," of"," communication"," as"," would"," be"," found"," in"," a"," traditional"," school"," setting","."," This"," makes"," it"," more"," difficult"," for"," students"," to"," form"," professional"," relationships"," and"," build"," their"," networks","."," Additionally",","," online"," learning"," does"," not"," involve"," face","-","to","-","face"," interactions"," with"," professors",","," which"," can"," limit"," the"," amount"," of"," feedback"," and"," support"," that"," is"," available",".","\n\n","Finally",","," there"," is"," also"," the"," possibility"," of"," limited"," access"," to"," academic"," resources","."," While"," some"," online"," courses"," offer"," videos"," and"," quizzes"," to"," enhance"," learning",","," these"," are"," not"," as"," comprehensive"," as"," the"," resources"," found"," in"," traditional"," classrooms","."," This"," can"," make"," it"," more"," difficult"," for"," students"," to"," fully"," grasp"," the"," material"," they"," are"," studying"," as"," well"," as"," retain"," information",".","\n\n","Despite"," the"," drawbacks"," of"," online"," learning",","," it"," can"," be"," a"," great"," way"," for"," students"," with"," limited"," time"," and"," resources"," to"," further"," their"," education","."," Additionally",","," online"," resources"," can"," be"," beneficial"," in"," enhancing"," learning"," and"," career"," opportunities","."," However",","," it"," is"," important"," for"," students"," to"," weigh"," the"," advantages"," and"," disadvantages"," of"," online"," learning"," before"," deciding"," which"," educational"," route"," to"," pursue","."," It"," is"," also"," important"," to"," note"," that"," attending"," a"," traditional"," school"," can"," also"," provide"," students"," with"," valuable"," networking"," opportunities"," as"," well"," as"," access"," to"," resources"," that"," can"," help"," enhance"," their"," learning"," and"," career"," opportunities","."," Ultimately",","," finding"," the"," best"," education"," solution"," will"," depend"," on"," the"," individual"," needs"," and"," objectives"," of"," each"," student","."," ","\n\n","Overall",","," online"," learning"," is"," an"," increasingly"," popular"," option"," for"," students"," with"," limited"," time"," and"," resources","."," Although"," there"," are"," disadvantages",","," it"," can"," also"," be"," a"," great"," way"," to"," pursue"," one","'","s"," educational"," goals",","," providing"," flexibility",","," cost"," effectiveness",","," and"," convenience","."," Additionally",","," online"," resources"," can"," be"," used"," to"," enhance"," learning"," and"," career"," opportunities","."," However",","," it"," is"," important"," for"," students"," to"," consider"," both"," the"," advantages"," and"," disadvantages"," of"," online"," learning"," before"," making"," their"," decision","."," Students"," should"," also"," consider"," the"," benefits"," of"," attending"," traditional"," schools"," if"," they"," want"," access"," to"," networking"," opportunities"," and"," more"," comprehensive"," educational"," resources","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"davinci","label":1}